OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1778328667
OL,3,CEx-prison officer jailed over illicit
OL,4,Ccontact with prisoner and supplying
OL,5,Cdrugs
OL,7,FA former Exeter prison officer has
OL,8,Fbeen jailed after pleading guilty to
OL,9,Fmisconduct in public office and
OL,10,Fsupplying class C drugs.
OL,12,FMonika Richards was sentenced to 14
OL,13,Fmonths in prison during a hearing at
OL,14,FExeter Crown Court on Tuesday 5 May.
OL,16,FThe court heard the 46-year-old was
OL,17,Fworking at HMP Exeter when she failed
OL,18,Fto inform the prison that a serving
OL,19,Fprisoner had a hidden mobile phone and
OL,20,Fshe had been communicating with him on
OL,21,Fthe device.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
